Package ca.mcgill.splendorserver.models.communicationbeans

Class SessionData

java.lang.Object
ca.mcgill.splendorserver.models.communicationbeans.SessionData
public class SessionData extends Object
Stores and manages LobbyService session data. Mainly used upon launching a session or otherwise communicating with LS.
